{
  "stem": "24615.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was so tired and everything, so I said yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We'll open a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I go into the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the first one they organized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were Zionist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I guess they were before the war Zionist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were older guys maybe, in the 40s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 1945.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went into the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A kibbutz, it was just in a house, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The plan was I should go and find more boys, and they should come in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll go to Israel from Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We go to Germany or what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I stayed maybe six months in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to another city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then from there, you know, we went in another city to cross the border to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We crossed, we went at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were waiting in a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a Polack, Polish soldier, two Polish soldiers-- there must have been maybe 100, 200 Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they asked for more money and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we said, you know, we're not going to give you more money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not like it was before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we start fighting them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Finally, they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we waited another two hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went, we crossed the border to Czechoslovakia, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took us maybe from 12 o'clock maybe to 7 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came into Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Slovakia, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, you know, we went in and they put some powder on us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if it were lice we had, it should kill out the sickness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed there I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was some kind of building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was the Joint Distribution.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was the Joint.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then from there, we walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
